rong></span></p>\n											</td>\n											<td style=\"width: 89px; height: 41px\">\n												<p align=\"center\">\n													<span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: bold 14px 宋体; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(156,68,3); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong>参加者</strong></span></p>\n											</td>\n											<td style=\"width: 121px; height: 41px\">\n												<p align=\"center\">\n													<span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: bold 14px 宋体; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(156,68,3); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong>责任人</strong></span></p>\n											</td>\n										</tr>\n										<tr>\n											<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 50px\">\n												<p align=\"center\">\n													<span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: bold 14px 宋体; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(156,68,3); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">1</span></p>\n											</td>\n											<td style=\"width: 77px\">\n												<p align=\"center\">\n													<span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: bold 14px 宋体; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(156,68,3); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">2月4日</span></p>\n											</td>\n											<td style=\"width: 98px\">\n												<p align=\"center\">\n													<span style=\"text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: bold 14px 宋体; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(15