<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td transparent=\"\">\n				<div 3.6pt=\"\">\n					<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n						<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n				</div>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">德育</span><em normal=\"\"><span auto=\"\">风景线</span></em></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 1.96=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\"><strong normal=\"\">DEYU</strong></span><strong normal=\"\">FENGJINGXIAN</strong></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td transparent=\"\">\n				<div>\n					<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n						<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">第1</span>?2版：关于在全校开展&ldquo;加强纪律教育，做文明一中人&rdquo;活动的通知</strong></span></p>\n					<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n						<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">第2</span>?4版：关于禁止学生在校内使用移动通讯工具等管理措施的通知</strong></span></p>\n					<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n						<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">第4</span>?5版：新洲一中校门管理规定</strong></span></p>\n					<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n						<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">第5</span>?7版：新洲一中校园文明礼貌用语规范</strong></span></p>\n				</div>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span yes=\"\">本期导读</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1&#4;clip_image007.jpg\" /></span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n	<br clear=\"all\" vglayout=\"\" />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 15.6pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">关于在全校开展&ldquo;加强纪律教育，做文明一中人&rdquo;</span></span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">活动的通知</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">各年级、各班：</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">为了进一步加强对学生的教育和管理，提升学校的教育教学和管理水平，为全校师生创设更为安宁、和谐的校园学习、生活环境，</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">&ldquo;创建和谐校园，共创文明城市&rdquo;，</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">促进我校学生综合素质和校园文化的内涵式发展，提升学校竞争的软实力，</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">经学校行政会研究决定，</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">教导处、校团委从</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月中旬至十月中旬在全校开展&ldquo;加强纪律教育，做文明一中人&rdquo;的活动。</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">希望各年级各班接到通知后加强学习，积极宣传并遵照执行。</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">具体方案如下：</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">一、总的目标：</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、以活动月为契机，对学生加强纪律和文明习惯的教育，促进学生正确的人生观和世界观的形成。积极宣传引导，在校园形成&ldquo;讲文明、讲礼貌、讲卫生&rdquo;的良好氛围。</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、培养学生正确的审美情趣，提倡清新自然、朴素大方、仪表端庄、文明高雅的着装，教育学生不在校园使用手机、不穿奇装异服进校园，自觉遵守学校的各项规章制度，提高学生的安全防范意识。</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">3</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、学习并使用校园文明礼貌用语，提高&ldquo;你好、请、谢谢、再见、对不起&rdquo;等礼貌用语的使用率，使学生懂得基本的学生礼仪礼节。</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">4</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、使&ldquo;净化校园、美化环境&rdquo;成为师生的自觉行动。保持教室、寝室、责任区、辅导室、办公室的净美，倡导并形成&ldquo;不乱丢垃圾&rdquo;&ldquo;把脚下的垃圾捡起来带走&rdquo;的校园新风尚。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">二、活动时间：9</span>月15??10月15日。</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">三、活动分为三个阶段：</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">（一）宣传学习阶段：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、各班认真学习新洲一中&ldquo;关于禁止学生在校使用移动通讯工具等管理措施的通知&rdquo;、&ldquo;新洲一中校门管理规定&rdquo;和&ldquo;新洲一中校园文明礼貌用语规范&rdquo;等相关文件精神，在师生中形成正确的舆论氛围，规范学生行为和文明礼貌用语。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、各班于</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">22</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">（周三）举行以&ldquo;加强纪律教育，做文明一中人&rdquo;为内容的主题班会。班会主题为：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1.</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">遵规守纪，从我做起；</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2.</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">说文明话、办文明事、做文明人；</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">3.</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">讲文明、讲礼貌、讲卫生。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">3</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、各班学习并制定班规和卫生条例制度，落实班级卫生责任制。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">（二）督查落实阶段</span></strong></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、各班自查学生仪表、抽烟、使用手机等违纪行为，自查&ldquo;文明礼貌用语&rdquo;班级使用情况，各班自查卫生、自行车摆放等方面存在的问题；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、教导处、团委会成立督查专班，加强校园文明礼貌督查，加大卫生检查评比力度。活动月特设</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">100</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">分的基本分，对不文明学生及时教育（情节严重的停课反省），扣除相应的活动月分数；对领导、老师反映的优秀学生和集体进行适当加分。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">3</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、采取班级自查与科任教师问卷调查相结合的形式，了解各班活动月落实情况。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">（三）总结表彰阶段</span></strong></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 2.0gd=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、督查结果即时通报，对优秀个人和集体进行奖励，对做得不好的进行批评。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 2.0gd=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、活动月期间的最终分数将按比例纳入班级量化总分。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">（四）主题班会检查工作安排</span></strong></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<table .5pt=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 5.4pt=\"\" auto=\"\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" medium=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr yes=\"\">\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">负责人</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">年级</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">检查工作人员</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr 1=\"\">\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" rowspan=\"3\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">刘成杰</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">高一</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">程盛怀</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">沈新华</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">文</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">夏春花</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr 2=\"\">\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">高二</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">刘骏军</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">黄志奇</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">程</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">亮</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">金</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">民</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr yes=\"\">\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">高三</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1&#4;clip_image009.jpg\" /><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">张正喜</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">刘双翼</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">黄维舜</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">沈明姣</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\" align=\"right\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">教导处</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">团委会</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 2.0=\"\" 5.25pt=\"\" align=\"right\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2010</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">年</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">12</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">学习材料一：</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">关于禁止学生在校使用移动通讯工具等管理措施的通知</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">尊敬的各位家长、亲爱的全体同学：</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">你们好！为了进一步做好学生管理和教育工作，为全体同学创设更为安宁、和谐的学习、生活环境，在广泛征求学生的意见，充分听取家长们建议和要求的基础上，学校行政会经过认真、慎重的研究后决定，继续加强学生管理，制定并实施禁止学生在学校使用移动通讯工具（手机、小灵通等）等有关管理措施。现正式向你们作出通报，希望全校同学认真执行，也希望得到各位家长的理解和大力支持。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">一、禁止学生在校使用手机。</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">对学生在校使用手机、小灵通等移动通讯工具所带来的负面影响问题，学生和很多家长一直都很关注，并多次口头和书面向学校提出好的意见。学生在校使用手机问题，也是社会关注的一个焦点问题，社会各界都参与了讨论，基本上都形成了禁止使用的共识，我省、我市也有许多学校都出台实施了禁止使用的具体规定。我校如何解决好这一问题，学校在全体同学中开展了广泛的讨论和问卷调查，从对回收问卷统计可以看到同学们对禁止使用手机等移动通讯工具是持积极支持态度的，回收问卷中只有几份是持反对意见，其主要理由是手机方便与家长联系。对这一合理要求，学校作出了积极反应，除确保校园现有IC</span>电话、201电话的正常使用外，我们与区电信局合作，在国庆节期间为全校每个学生寝室安装两部201电话，确保学生与家长的信息交流。综合、归纳同学们赞成禁止学生在校使用手机的意见，主要有如下几个方面：</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">1</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">．学生现在是纯消费者，应提倡生活节俭。作为子女，不能为家庭创造收入，但可以降低消费，借此尽量减小父母的经济压力。这也可以算是对父母养育之恩的一种报答。购买与使用手机、小灵通完全与这一道德原则相背离。有些同学为手机问题跟家长闹得很不愉快，实在是有违做子女的道德和责任。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">2</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">．高中正处于人生成长发展的重要阶段，学生要自觉培养健康的心理素质。有的的同学有手机或向家长要手机，并不是确实需要，而是虚荣心作怪，是想追随社会潮流，想以此在同学们面前炫耀。少数同学的这种行为，也容易在同学们中引起攀比之风，不利于同学们形成健康的良好心态。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">3</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">．学生应集中精力，专心学习。很多同学使用手机，传递的绝大多数是与学习无关的内容，容易分散学习注意力。特别是与一些品行不良的人经常通话和相互传递一些不健康甚至黄色、暴力、诈骗方面的信息，对学生成长造成的危害就更为严重了。有时在上课或是自习的时候手机铃声突然响起，既让自己违纪，又破坏了课堂气氛，耽误了同学们的学习。即使是让很少人知道自己的号码，且设为振动，但有些运营商的短信也会突如其来，使自己的学习注意力受到影响。还有的同学经常在手机上玩游戏，既损伤了视力，又浪费了宝贵的学习时间。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">4</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">．手机助长了考试作弊的歪风邪气，充当了破坏诚信美德的帮凶。有的同学遇事经常通过手机邀约其他同学甚至是社会不良人员，插手同学纠纷，以致扩大事态，造成严重的后果。这在我校以及其他学校都有惨痛的教训。可以说手机使他们错误地处理同学之间矛盾成为了可能，甚至是有直接的反面推动作用。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">5</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">．手机属贵重物品且易于损坏。一旦丢失或损坏，对学习、生活情绪影响非常大。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">6</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">．手机是否借给别的同学也不好把握。借了，多用话费不说，如果不慎损坏、丢失或被老师收走，处理起来就非常麻烦；有时借给别人用，还容易无端卷入一些是非和纠葛中，徒增烦恼。不借，别人说你小气：总之，借与不借都影响同学关系。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">从以上同学们列举的学生在校使用手机的各种弊端表明对此强化管理已是人心所向，势在必行了。学校经研究决定：</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">禁止学生在校使用手机等一切移动通讯工具。如有违反，第一次予以收缴，对其进行严肃批评，并通知家长到校领取收缴物品；第二次没收所用通讯工具，并视认错态度，处记过或以上处分；第三次没收所用通讯工具，并处留校察看直至劝其退学的处分。</span></strong></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">二、禁止学生骑摩托车、电动车进校园。</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">学校面积和停车位置有限，师生人数多、自行车多，容易发生交通安全问题，为了你孩子和他人的安全，请不要让孩子骑摩托车、电动车上学。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">三、禁止学生染发、烫发、发型怪异、男生留长发（前遮眉眼，侧遮耳脸，后遮领脖）；禁止学生戴耳环（耳钉）、戒指、项链等首饰；禁止穿着怪异、不得体服饰。学校</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">提倡清新自然、朴素大方、仪表端庄、文明高雅。下一阶段学校将逐个清理，对不符合要求的禁止进校。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">四、</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">禁止无家长亲属陪读而私自外出租房住宿。</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">安全责任，警钟长鸣。我校学生手册上有规定，在外租房必须经过以下程序：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1.</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">符合规定和要求的，学生提出书面申请；</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2.</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">家长和班主任当面协商同意，签订安全责任书；</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">3.</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">报年级德育主任审批并存档（班主任、年级德育主任各留一份）。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">五</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">关于午休纪律规定：</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">不会休息，就不会学习。在作息安排上，学校保证了学生应有的睡眠时间（晚上</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">10</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">20</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">至次日</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">6</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">00</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">，中午</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">00?2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">00</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">），即使是国庆之后，我校仍然安排有午睡时间。为了安全和便于管理，特作如下要求：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、学校原则上要求住读生、走读生都</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">在教室午休，各年级各班安排班主任、副班主任午休值日，学校安排相关领导和教师巡查。</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、中午</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">00??2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">00</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">为午休时间。校门封闭，禁止学生随意进出，走读生必须在</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">10</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">之前进校。</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">3</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、确有特殊原因需在家午休的走读生，必须写好在家午休申请，家长与班主任协商并签字后方可在家午休。家长要提醒孩子按时到校，注意交通安全。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 3.68gd=\"\" 38.65pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">新 洲 一 中</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 1.97gd=\"\" 20.7pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">2010</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">年9</span>月1日</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 1.97gd=\"\" 20.7pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1&#4;clip_image011.png\" /></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 1.97gd=\"\" 20.7pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 1.7pt=\"\">学习材料二</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 1.7pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">新洲一中校门管理规定</span></span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">一、学生出入校门要注意安全，服从管理，遵守礼仪。凡衣着不整、佩戴饰品、烫发染发、长发（男生）者，一律不得入校。讲究卫生，不得将一次性餐具或包装带入校园。住读学生非放假时间，一律不得出校。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">．进校</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">早晨到校，从开启的校门顺序进入；迟到者，将自行车<span 0.1pt=\"\">停放在指定位置后，步行入校。下午进校时间为</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">12</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">:<span 0.1pt=\"\">20?13</span>:<span 0.1pt=\"\">10</span></span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">和</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">14</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">:<span 0.1pt=\"\">00??14</span>:<span 0.1pt=\"\">20</span></span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">两个时段，其它时间不得进入；入校礼仪是：车挂牌，人佩证，推车走，入校门。无牌无证，经班主任或老师证实后，方可进入。早、晚餐后入校，须佩戴学生证、出示出入证，否则不得进校。放假返校要求按中午规定执行。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">．出校</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">不到规定时间学生一律不得出校。中午、晚上放学，学生统一由西大门学生通道出校。早、晚餐时间出校，须佩戴学生证，出示出入证，经查验后方可出校；出校后在外摊点就餐的，第一次警告，第二次没收出入证并告知班主任。学生因事、因病出校，必须持有班主任或科任老师签名的出入凭条，并由老师电话通知保卫人员（大门</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">86916474</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">，后门</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">86916544</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">）或亲自送至校门，方可出校。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">二、家长来校</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">每周六为家长接待日，家长可在放学后按保卫人员的统一指挥步行入校。其它时间来校，须按下述第三条规定办理有关手续。</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">家长接送孩子，一律不得进入校园；等候时间，须保持安静，爱护环境卫生，按指定位置停放车辆，确保学生出入安全畅通。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">三、因事来校、来访必须办理入校手续，具体为：先自行与被访者电话联系并交保卫人员接听证实或由被访者到校门迎接，然后填写来访登记单，经允许后步行入校。离校时，须将来访登记单第二联交保卫人员查验后，方可离开。公务来校车辆登记入校后须减速慢行并按指定地点停放。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">四、组团来访、租用场地、组织活动按规定先申报，后审批，否则一律不得进入。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">五、非规定的校园对外开放时间，谢绝一切人员入校游玩、锻炼。放假时间，本校在读学生主动出示学生证，经保卫人员查验同意后，可进校锻炼。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">六、学校大门每天早晨</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">5:30</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">开门，晚上</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">11:30</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">锁门。后门每天早晨</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">6:00</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">开门，晚上</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">11:00</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">锁门；</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">后门每天上午</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">8:30</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">－</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">11:00</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">，下午</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2:30</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">－</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">4:10</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">锁门，保卫人员离岗休息。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 3.68gd=\"\" 38.65pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">新 洲 一 中</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 1.97gd=\"\" 20.7pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">2010</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">年8</span>月25日</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1&#4;clip_image013.jpg\" /></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">学习材料三</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">新洲一中校园文明礼貌用语规范</span></span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">第?部分在教室里的礼貌用语</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\">(</strong><strong normal=\"\">一)教学前后</strong></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1、课前小预备，教师应到教室门口巡视，室内学生做好课前准备。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2、当响起上课铃声，教师走到讲台前，立正后说&ldquo;上课&rdquo;，班长或值日生喊&ldquo;起立&rdquo;，教师喊&ldquo;同学们好&rdquo;，全体学生应喊&ldquo;老师好&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3、下课铃声响后，教师说&ldquo;下课&rdquo;，全体学生起立，教师巡视后喊&ldquo;同学们再见&rdquo;，学生齐声应&ldquo;老师再见&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4、学生立正后等教师离开讲桌出门时，班里学生方可离开座位。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\">（二）教学过程中</strong></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1、课堂上教师向学生提问题时，学生应积极思考，知道的同学都应举手准备回答。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2、当教师指名回答问题时，学生起立回答教师所提出的问题。学生回答问题后，教师应向学生说声&ldquo;请坐&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3、学生听课过程中有疑问时，先举手，经教师许可，方可发言。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4、当学生因事迟到时，应站在教室门口喊声&ldquo;报告&rdquo;，得到教师回答&ldquo;请进&rdquo;方可进教室。</span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">第二部分在办公室里礼貌用语</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1、学生进办公室前先敲门后立正喊&ldquo;报告&rdquo;，室内有关教师要回答&ldquo;请进&rdquo; 。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2、学生轻轻步入教师办公桌前，交、取作业或请教问题时要立正，未经教师允许不得坐下。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3、学生接受教师递送物品时，要用双手，并说&ldquo;谢谢&rdquo; 。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4、教师与学生谈话结束时，学生向教师行鞠躬礼，教师应点头还礼，并说&ldquo;再见&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">第三部分在宿舍里礼貌用语</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1、来宾进宿舍楼，迎面遇见学生，学生应主动打招呼&ldquo;老师（首长）好&rdquo;，来宾离开宿舍楼，学生也应主动告别说&ldquo;老师（首长）再见&rdquo;或&ldquo;老师（首长）慢走&rdquo; 。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2、来宾来到房间前，先敲门，室内学生要说&ldquo;请进&rdquo;或说&ldquo;对不起，稍等&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3、学生从室内开门后，室内其他学生起立，见到来宾笑说&ldquo;老师（首长）好&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4、当来宾说&ldquo;同学们请坐&rdquo;，室内学生说&ldquo;老师（首长）请坐&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">5、当来宾跟学生谈话结束，起立要走时，来宾说&ldquo;同学们再见&rdquo;，学生起立说&ldquo;老师（首长）再见。&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">6、校领导或教职工进宿舍，学生也应主动打招呼或点头致意，相应问好。</span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">第四部分在校园内外礼貌用语</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">1</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、学生在校内外，迎面遇见认识的教职工时，应主动打招呼&ldquo;&times;&times;</span>老师好!&rdquo;或&ldquo;&times;&times;师傅好!&rdquo;如果迎面遇见不认识的教职工，应点头致意。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">2</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、在校园内，迎面遇见不认识的来宾，而来宾又没有主动跟学生打招呼，这时学生要微笑点头致意，以礼相待，如果来宾主动跟学生打招呼，比如&ldquo;</span>同学们好&rdquo;，学生要立正，以礼相谢对方说&ldquo;老师(首长)好&rdquo;。如果来宾询问同学有关情况，学生不知道的，应用亲切温和的语调回答对方说&ldquo;对不起，我不了解(或我不知道)&rdquo;，如果学生与来宾交谈结束，在临别时应说&ldquo;老师(首长)再见&rdquo;如果是晚上，应该说&ldquo;晚安&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">3</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、如果来宾要召开部分学生座谈会，参加会议的学生要先敲门，后立正，说&ldquo;</span>报告&rdquo;，来宾说&ldquo;请进&rdquo;。学生较轻走到来宾跟前要立正，未经来宾允许，不得坐下。学生接受来宾采访，坐、立、写字姿势要端正，谈话语调要恳切、温和。如果来宾赠送学生物品，学生接收时，要用双手，并说&ldquo;谢谢&rdquo;。学生与来宾交谈结束，临别时主动向来宾行鞠躬礼，并说&ldquo;老师（首长）再见&rdquo; 。</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">日常文明礼貌用语集锦</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1、见面问候语：您好；早上好；晚上好；您好，见到您很高兴；&times;&times;最近很忙吧！请转达我对他的问候！</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2、分手辞别语：再见；再会；祝您一路顺风；希望不久的将来还能在这里欢迎您。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3、求助于人语：请；请问；请帮忙；请帮助我一下；请多指教。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4、受人相助语：谢谢；麻烦你了；非常感谢！</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">5、得到感谢语：别客气；不用谢。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">6、打扰别人语：请原谅；对不起；给您添麻烦了；让您受累了。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">7、听到致歉语：不要紧；没关系；您不必介意。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">8、接待来客语：请进；请坐；请喝茶；再次见到您，真是十分高兴；欢迎光临。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">9、送别客人语：再见；慢走；欢迎再来。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">10、无力助人语：抱歉；实在对不起；请原谅。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">11</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、礼称别人语：老师；同志；先生；小姐；师傅；朋友。</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">12</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、提醒别人语：请您小心；请您注意；请您别急。</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">13</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、提醒行人语：请您注意安全；过路请走行人道。</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">14</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、慰问语：您辛苦了；让您受累了；给您添麻烦了。</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">15</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、赞美语：您干得很好；太棒了；您真了不起；这太美了。</span></span></p>\n<p -2.0=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">16</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、征询语：我能为您做些什么吗？这样会不会打扰您？您还有别的事情吗？请借光；请您让一让好吗？</span></span></p>\n<p -2.0=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">17</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、道歉语：很抱歉！这件事实在没有办法做到；真不好意思&hellip;&hellip;；真对不起，让您久等了！对不起，打扰了！对不起，请稍候！</span></span></p>\n<p -2.0=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">18</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、应答语：行，请您稍候；好，马上就来；您不必客气，这是我应该做的；不用谢，照顾不周的地方请您多多包涵；请您吩咐。</span></span></p>\n<p -2.0=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">19</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、排队语：请大家自觉排队；请您排队好吗？</span></span></p>\n<p -2.0=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">20</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、接打电话语：您好！我是&times;&times;&times;</span>，请讲话。谢谢，再见。</span></p>\n<p -2.0=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">公民基本道德规范</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">爱国守法 　明礼诚信　团结友善 　勤俭自强　敬业奉献</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">武汉市市民&ldquo;十不&rdquo;行为规范</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">一、不随地吐痰；二、不乱倒乱扔废弃物；<br />\n	　　三、不乱贴乱画；四、不乱停放车辆；<br />\n	　　五、不乱穿马路；六、不乱搭乱盖；<br />\n	　　七、不损坏公共设施；八、不损害花草树木；<br />\n	　　九、不在公共场所吸烟十、不说脏话粗话</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1&#4;clip_image015.jpg\" /><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">&ldquo;三不&rdquo;与&ldquo;三管住&rdquo;</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">　　<span 10.5pt=\"\">一、不乱穿马路，管住自己的脚。<br />\n	　　二、不乱扔废弃物，管住自己的手。<br />\n	　　三、不说脏话粗话，管住自己的口。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">附：&ldquo;加强纪律教育，做文明一中人&rdquo;</span>督查工作安排</span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<table .5pt=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 5.4pt=\"\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" medium=\"\" solid=\"\" width=\"547\" windowtext=\"\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr exactly=\"\">\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">时</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">间</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">带队领导</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">参</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">加</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">人</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">员</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr exactly=\"\">\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">22</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">周</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">三</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">程盛怀</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">文</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">夏春花</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">郭大玉</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡跃进</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">方探锋</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr exactly=\"\">\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">23</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">周</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">四</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">沈新华</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">刘幼平</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">李红杰</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">郭大玉</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡跃进</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">方探锋</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr exactly=\"\">\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">24</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">周</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">五</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">张正喜</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">程</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">亮</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">李红杰</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">郭大玉</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡跃进</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">方探锋</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr exactly=\"\">\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">25</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">周</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">六</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">刘俊军</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">文</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">黄志奇</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">郭大玉</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡跃进</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">方探锋</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr exactly=\"\">\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">26</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">周</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">程盛怀</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">刘幼平</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">李红杰</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">郭大玉</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡跃进</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">方探锋</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr exactly=\"\">\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">27</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">周</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">一</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">刘双翼</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" 1.5=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">黄维舜</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">黄志奇</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">郭大玉</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡跃进</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">方探锋</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr exactly=\"\">\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">28</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">周</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">二</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">沈新华</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">刘幼平</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">郭大玉</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡跃进</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">方探锋</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">于志勇</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">说明：</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 2.0gd=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">．严禁学生在校园使用手机等移动通讯工具，禁止学生在教学区使用</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">MP3</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">MP4</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">等娱乐工具。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 2.0gd=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">．中午午休、下午放学、晚自习放学为带队集中巡查时间段（可在教导处集中），保卫巡逻人员近段时间全天候加强督查，特别是</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">5</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">00</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">?</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">30</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 2.0gd=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">3</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">．发现违纪情况，首先没收手机、</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">MP3</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">MP4</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">等物品，下发《违纪通知单》，然后通知班主任请家长来校带违纪学生回家教育三天，并全校通报批评，扣除该班</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">5</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">分。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1&#4;clip_image017.jpg\" /></span></p>\n','2','7','46',28,NULL,'2','1','2015-03-04 14:06:33','2015-03-04 14:06:33'),(131,'德育风景线 第58期','2010-09-12','1','<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>武汉市新洲区第一中学</strong></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">教导处团 委</span><strong normal=\"\">主办</strong></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\">2010</strong><strong normal=\"\">年9月12日</strong><strong normal=\"\">第58期 共8版</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img cropbottom=\"24116f\" cropright=\"1396f\" src=\"file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1&#4;clip_image003.png\" /></span></p>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td transparent=\"\">\n				<div 3.6pt=\"\">\n					<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n						<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n				</div>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">德育</span><em normal=\"\"><span auto=\"\">风景线</span></em></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 1.96=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\"><strong normal=\"\">DEYU</strong></span><strong normal=\"\">FENGJINGXIAN</strong></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td transparent=\"\">\n				<div>\n					<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n						<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">第1</span>?2版：关于在全校开展&ldquo;加强纪律教育，做文明一中人&rdquo;活动的通知</strong></span></p>\n					<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n						<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">第2</span>?4版：关于禁止学生在校内使用移动通讯工具等管理措施的通知</strong></span></p>\n					<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n						<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">第4</span>?5版：新洲一中校门管理规定</strong></span></p>\n					<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n						<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">第5</span>?7版：新洲一中校园文明礼貌用语规范</strong></span></p>\n				</div>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span yes=\"\">本期导读</span></span></p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1&#4;clip_image007.jpg\" /></span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n	<br clear=\"all\" vglayout=\"\" />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 15.6pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">关于在全校开展&ldquo;加强纪律教育，做文明一中人&rdquo;</span></span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">活动的通知</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">各年级、各班：</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">为了进一步加强对学生的教育和管理，提升学校的教育教学和管理水平，为全校师生创设更为安宁、和谐的校园学习、生活环境，</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">&ldquo;创建和谐校园，共创文明城市&rdquo;，</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">促进我校学生综合素质和校园文化的内涵式发展，提升学校竞争的软实力，</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">经学校行政会研究决定，</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">教导处、校团委从</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月中旬至十月中旬在全校开展&ldquo;加强纪律教育，做文明一中人&rdquo;的活动。</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">希望各年级各班接到通知后加强学习，积极宣传并遵照执行。</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">具体方案如下：</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">一、总的目标：</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、以活动月为契机，对学生加强纪律和文明习惯的教育，促进学生正确的人生观和世界观的形成。积极宣传引导，在校园形成&ldquo;讲文明、讲礼貌、讲卫生&rdquo;的良好氛围。</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、培养学生正确的审美情趣，提倡清新自然、朴素大方、仪表端庄、文明高雅的着装，教育学生不在校园使用手机、不穿奇装异服进校园，自觉遵守学校的各项规章制度，提高学生的安全防范意识。</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">3</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、学习并使用校园文明礼貌用语，提高&ldquo;你好、请、谢谢、再见、对不起&rdquo;等礼貌用语的使用率，使学生懂得基本的学生礼仪礼节。</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">4</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、使&ldquo;净化校园、美化环境&rdquo;成为师生的自觉行动。保持教室、寝室、责任区、辅导室、办公室的净美，倡导并形成&ldquo;不乱丢垃圾&rdquo;&ldquo;把脚下的垃圾捡起来带走&rdquo;的校园新风尚。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">二、活动时间：9</span>月15??10月15日。</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">三、活动分为三个阶段：</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">（一）宣传学习阶段：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、各班认真学习新洲一中&ldquo;关于禁止学生在校使用移动通讯工具等管理措施的通知&rdquo;、&ldquo;新洲一中校门管理规定&rdquo;和&ldquo;新洲一中校园文明礼貌用语规范&rdquo;等相关文件精神，在师生中形成正确的舆论氛围，规范学生行为和文明礼貌用语。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、各班于</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">22</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">（周三）举行以&ldquo;加强纪律教育，做文明一中人&rdquo;为内容的主题班会。班会主题为：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1.</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">遵规守纪，从我做起；</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2.</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">说文明话、办文明事、做文明人；</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">3.</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">讲文明、讲礼貌、讲卫生。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">3</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、各班学习并制定班规和卫生条例制度，落实班级卫生责任制。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">（二）督查落实阶段</span></strong></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、各班自查学生仪表、抽烟、使用手机等违纪行为，自查&ldquo;文明礼貌用语&rdquo;班级使用情况，各班自查卫生、自行车摆放等方面存在的问题；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、教导处、团委会成立督查专班，加强校园文明礼貌督查，加大卫生检查评比力度。活动月特设</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">100</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">分的基本分，对不文明学生及时教育（情节严重的停课反省），扣除相应的活动月分数；对领导、老师反映的优秀学生和集体进行适当加分。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">3</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、采取班级自查与科任教师问卷调查相结合的形式，了解各班活动月落实情况。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">（三）总结表彰阶段</span></strong></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 2.0gd=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、督查结果即时通报，对优秀个人和集体进行奖励，对做得不好的进行批评。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 2.0gd=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、活动月期间的最终分数将按比例纳入班级量化总分。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">（四）主题班会检查工作安排</span></strong></span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<table .5pt=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 5.4pt=\"\" auto=\"\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" medium=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr yes=\"\">\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">负责人</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">年级</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">检查工作人员</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr 1=\"\">\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" rowspan=\"3\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">刘成杰</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">高一</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">程盛怀</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">沈新华</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">文</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">夏春花</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr 2=\"\">\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">高二</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">刘骏军</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">黄志奇</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">程</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">亮</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">金</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">民</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr yes=\"\">\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">高三</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td .5pt=\"\" 1pt=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1&#4;clip_image009.jpg\" /><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">张正喜</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">刘双翼</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">黄维舜</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">沈明姣</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\" align=\"right\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">教导处</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">团委会</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 2.0=\"\" 5.25pt=\"\" align=\"right\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2010</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">年</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">12</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">学习材料一：</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">关于禁止学生在校使用移动通讯工具等管理措施的通知</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">尊敬的各位家长、亲爱的全体同学：</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">你们好！为了进一步做好学生管理和教育工作，为全体同学创设更为安宁、和谐的学习、生活环境，在广泛征求学生的意见，充分听取家长们建议和要求的基础上，学校行政会经过认真、慎重的研究后决定，继续加强学生管理，制定并实施禁止学生在学校使用移动通讯工具（手机、小灵通等）等有关管理措施。现正式向你们作出通报，希望全校同学认真执行，也希望得到各位家长的理解和大力支持。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">一、禁止学生在校使用手机。</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">对学生在校使用手机、小灵通等移动通讯工具所带来的负面影响问题，学生和很多家长一直都很关注，并多次口头和书面向学校提出好的意见。学生在校使用手机问题，也是社会关注的一个焦点问题，社会各界都参与了讨论，基本上都形成了禁止使用的共识，我省、我市也有许多学校都出台实施了禁止使用的具体规定。我校如何解决好这一问题，学校在全体同学中开展了广泛的讨论和问卷调查，从对回收问卷统计可以看到同学们对禁止使用手机等移动通讯工具是持积极支持态度的，回收问卷中只有几份是持反对意见，其主要理由是手机方便与家长联系。对这一合理要求，学校作出了积极反应，除确保校园现有IC</span>电话、201电话的正常使用外，我们与区电信局合作，在国庆节期间为全校每个学生寝室安装两部201电话，确保学生与家长的信息交流。综合、归纳同学们赞成禁止学生在校使用手机的意见，主要有如下几个方面：</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">1</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">．学生现在是纯消费者，应提倡生活节俭。作为子女，不能为家庭创造收入，但可以降低消费，借此尽量减小父母的经济压力。这也可以算是对父母养育之恩的一种报答。购买与使用手机、小灵通完全与这一道德原则相背离。有些同学为手机问题跟家长闹得很不愉快，实在是有违做子女的道德和责任。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">2</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">．高中正处于人生成长发展的重要阶段，学生要自觉培养健康的心理素质。有的的同学有手机或向家长要手机，并不是确实需要，而是虚荣心作怪，是想追随社会潮流，想以此在同学们面前炫耀。少数同学的这种行为，也容易在同学们中引起攀比之风，不利于同学们形成健康的良好心态。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">3</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">．学生应集中精力，专心学习。很多同学使用手机，传递的绝大多数是与学习无关的内容，容易分散学习注意力。特别是与一些品行不良的人经常通话和相互传递一些不健康甚至黄色、暴力、诈骗方面的信息，对学生成长造成的危害就更为严重了。有时在上课或是自习的时候手机铃声突然响起，既让自己违纪，又破坏了课堂气氛，耽误了同学们的学习。即使是让很少人知道自己的号码，且设为振动，但有些运营商的短信也会突如其来，使自己的学习注意力受到影响。还有的同学经常在手机上玩游戏，既损伤了视力，又浪费了宝贵的学习时间。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">4</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">．手机助长了考试作弊的歪风邪气，充当了破坏诚信美德的帮凶。有的同学遇事经常通过手机邀约其他同学甚至是社会不良人员，插手同学纠纷，以致扩大事态，造成严重的后果。这在我校以及其他学校都有惨痛的教训。可以说手机使他们错误地处理同学之间矛盾成为了可能，甚至是有直接的反面推动作用。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">5</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">．手机属贵重物品且易于损坏。一旦丢失或损坏，对学习、生活情绪影响非常大。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">6</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">．手机是否借给别的同学也不好把握。借了，多用话费不说，如果不慎损坏、丢失或被老师收走，处理起来就非常麻烦；有时借给别人用，还容易无端卷入一些是非和纠葛中，徒增烦恼。不借，别人说你小气：总之，借与不借都影响同学关系。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">从以上同学们列举的学生在校使用手机的各种弊端表明对此强化管理已是人心所向，势在必行了。学校经研究决定：</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">禁止学生在校使用手机等一切移动通讯工具。如有违反，第一次予以收缴，对其进行严肃批评，并通知家长到校领取收缴物品；第二次没收所用通讯工具，并视认错态度，处记过或以上处分；第三次没收所用通讯工具，并处留校察看直至劝其退学的处分。</span></strong></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">二、禁止学生骑摩托车、电动车进校园。</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">学校面积和停车位置有限，师生人数多、自行车多，容易发生交通安全问题，为了你孩子和他人的安全，请不要让孩子骑摩托车、电动车上学。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">三、禁止学生染发、烫发、发型怪异、男生留长发（前遮眉眼，侧遮耳脸，后遮领脖）；禁止学生戴耳环（耳钉）、戒指、项链等首饰；禁止穿着怪异、不得体服饰。学校</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">提倡清新自然、朴素大方、仪表端庄、文明高雅。下一阶段学校将逐个清理，对不符合要求的禁止进校。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">四、</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">禁止无家长亲属陪读而私自外出租房住宿。</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">安全责任，警钟长鸣。我校学生手册上有规定，在外租房必须经过以下程序：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1.</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">符合规定和要求的，学生提出书面申请；</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2.</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">家长和班主任当面协商同意，签订安全责任书；</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">3.</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">报年级德育主任审批并存档（班主任、年级德育主任各留一份）。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">五</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">关于午休纪律规定：</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">不会休息，就不会学习。在作息安排上，学校保证了学生应有的睡眠时间（晚上</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">10</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">20</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">至次日</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">6</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">00</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">，中午</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">00?2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">00</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">），即使是国庆之后，我校仍然安排有午睡时间。为了安全和便于管理，特作如下要求：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、学校原则上要求住读生、走读生都</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">在教室午休，各年级各班安排班主任、副班主任午休值日，学校安排相关领导和教师巡查。</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、中午</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">00??2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">00</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">为午休时间。校门封闭，禁止学生随意进出，走读生必须在</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">10</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">之前进校。</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">3</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、确有特殊原因需在家午休的走读生，必须写好在家午休申请，家长与班主任协商并签字后方可在家午休。家长要提醒孩子按时到校，注意交通安全。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 3.68gd=\"\" 38.65pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">新 洲 一 中</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 1.97gd=\"\" 20.7pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">2010</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">年9</span>月1日</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 1.97gd=\"\" 20.7pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1&#4;clip_image011.png\" /></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 1.97gd=\"\" 20.7pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 1.7pt=\"\">学习材料二</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 1.7pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">新洲一中校门管理规定</span></span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">一、学生出入校门要注意安全，服从管理，遵守礼仪。凡衣着不整、佩戴饰品、烫发染发、长发（男生）者，一律不得入校。讲究卫生，不得将一次性餐具或包装带入校园。住读学生非放假时间，一律不得出校。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">．进校</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">早晨到校，从开启的校门顺序进入；迟到者，将自行车<span 0.1pt=\"\">停放在指定位置后，步行入校。下午进校时间为</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">12</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">:<span 0.1pt=\"\">20?13</span>:<span 0.1pt=\"\">10</span></span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">和</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">14</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">:<span 0.1pt=\"\">00??14</span>:<span 0.1pt=\"\">20</span></span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">两个时段，其它时间不得进入；入校礼仪是：车挂牌，人佩证，推车走，入校门。无牌无证，经班主任或老师证实后，方可进入。早、晚餐后入校，须佩戴学生证、出示出入证，否则不得进校。放假返校要求按中午规定执行。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">．出校</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">不到规定时间学生一律不得出校。中午、晚上放学，学生统一由西大门学生通道出校。早、晚餐时间出校，须佩戴学生证，出示出入证，经查验后方可出校；出校后在外摊点就餐的，第一次警告，第二次没收出入证并告知班主任。学生因事、因病出校，必须持有班主任或科任老师签名的出入凭条，并由老师电话通知保卫人员（大门</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">86916474</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">，后门</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">86916544</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">）或亲自送至校门，方可出校。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">二、家长来校</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">每周六为家长接待日，家长可在放学后按保卫人员的统一指挥步行入校。其它时间来校，须按下述第三条规定办理有关手续。</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">家长接送孩子，一律不得进入校园；等候时间，须保持安静，爱护环境卫生，按指定位置停放车辆，确保学生出入安全畅通。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">三、因事来校、来访必须办理入校手续，具体为：先自行与被访者电话联系并交保卫人员接听证实或由被访者到校门迎接，然后填写来访登记单，经允许后步行入校。离校时，须将来访登记单第二联交保卫人员查验后，方可离开。公务来校车辆登记入校后须减速慢行并按指定地点停放。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">四、组团来访、租用场地、组织活动按规定先申报，后审批，否则一律不得进入。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">五、非规定的校园对外开放时间，谢绝一切人员入校游玩、锻炼。放假时间，本校在读学生主动出示学生证，经保卫人员查验同意后，可进校锻炼。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">六、学校大门每天早晨</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">5:30</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">开门，晚上</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">11:30</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">锁门。后门每天早晨</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">6:00</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">开门，晚上</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">11:00</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">锁门；</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">后门每天上午</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">8:30</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">－</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">11:00</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">，下午</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2:30</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">－</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">4:10</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">锁门，保卫人员离岗休息。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 3.68gd=\"\" 38.65pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">新 洲 一 中</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 1.97gd=\"\" 20.7pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">2010</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">年8</span>月25日</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1&#4;clip_image013.jpg\" /></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">学习材料三</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">新洲一中校园文明礼貌用语规范</span></span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">第?部分在教室里的礼貌用语</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\">(</strong><strong normal=\"\">一)教学前后</strong></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1、课前小预备，教师应到教室门口巡视，室内学生做好课前准备。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2、当响起上课铃声，教师走到讲台前，立正后说&ldquo;上课&rdquo;，班长或值日生喊&ldquo;起立&rdquo;，教师喊&ldquo;同学们好&rdquo;，全体学生应喊&ldquo;老师好&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3、下课铃声响后，教师说&ldquo;下课&rdquo;，全体学生起立，教师巡视后喊&ldquo;同学们再见&rdquo;，学生齐声应&ldquo;老师再见&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4、学生立正后等教师离开讲桌出门时，班里学生方可离开座位。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\">（二）教学过程中</strong></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1、课堂上教师向学生提问题时，学生应积极思考，知道的同学都应举手准备回答。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2、当教师指名回答问题时，学生起立回答教师所提出的问题。学生回答问题后，教师应向学生说声&ldquo;请坐&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3、学生听课过程中有疑问时，先举手，经教师许可，方可发言。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4、当学生因事迟到时，应站在教室门口喊声&ldquo;报告&rdquo;，得到教师回答&ldquo;请进&rdquo;方可进教室。</span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">第二部分在办公室里礼貌用语</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1、学生进办公室前先敲门后立正喊&ldquo;报告&rdquo;，室内有关教师要回答&ldquo;请进&rdquo; 。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2、学生轻轻步入教师办公桌前，交、取作业或请教问题时要立正，未经教师允许不得坐下。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3、学生接受教师递送物品时，要用双手，并说&ldquo;谢谢&rdquo; 。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4、教师与学生谈话结束时，学生向教师行鞠躬礼，教师应点头还礼，并说&ldquo;再见&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">第三部分在宿舍里礼貌用语</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1、来宾进宿舍楼，迎面遇见学生，学生应主动打招呼&ldquo;老师（首长）好&rdquo;，来宾离开宿舍楼，学生也应主动告别说&ldquo;老师（首长）再见&rdquo;或&ldquo;老师（首长）慢走&rdquo; 。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2、来宾来到房间前，先敲门，室内学生要说&ldquo;请进&rdquo;或说&ldquo;对不起，稍等&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3、学生从室内开门后，室内其他学生起立，见到来宾笑说&ldquo;老师（首长）好&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4、当来宾说&ldquo;同学们请坐&rdquo;，室内学生说&ldquo;老师（首长）请坐&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">5、当来宾跟学生谈话结束，起立要走时，来宾说&ldquo;同学们再见&rdquo;，学生起立说&ldquo;老师（首长）再见。&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">6、校领导或教职工进宿舍，学生也应主动打招呼或点头致意，相应问好。</span></p>\n<p .5gd=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\" align=\"center\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">第四部分在校园内外礼貌用语</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">1</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、学生在校内外，迎面遇见认识的教职工时，应主动打招呼&ldquo;&times;&times;</span>老师好!&rdquo;或&ldquo;&times;&times;师傅好!&rdquo;如果迎面遇见不认识的教职工，应点头致意。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">2</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、在校园内，迎面遇见不认识的来宾，而来宾又没有主动跟学生打招呼，这时学生要微笑点头致意，以礼相待，如果来宾主动跟学生打招呼，比如&ldquo;</span>同学们好&rdquo;，学生要立正，以礼相谢对方说&ldquo;老师(首长)好&rdquo;。如果来宾询问同学有关情况，学生不知道的，应用亲切温和的语调回答对方说&ldquo;对不起，我不了解(或我不知道)&rdquo;，如果学生与来宾交谈结束，在临别时应说&ldquo;老师(首长)再见&rdquo;如果是晚上，应该说&ldquo;晚安&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">3</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、如果来宾要召开部分学生座谈会，参加会议的学生要先敲门，后立正，说&ldquo;</span>报告&rdquo;，来宾说&ldquo;请进&rdquo;。学生较轻走到来宾跟前要立正，未经来宾允许，不得坐下。学生接受来宾采访，坐、立、写字姿势要端正，谈话语调要恳切、温和。如果来宾赠送学生物品，学生接收时，要用双手，并说&ldquo;谢谢&rdquo;。学生与来宾交谈结束，临别时主动向来宾行鞠躬礼，并说&ldquo;老师（首长）再见&rdquo; 。</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">日常文明礼貌用语集锦</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1、见面问候语：您好；早上好；晚上好；您好，见到您很高兴；&times;&times;最近很忙吧！请转达我对他的问候！</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2、分手辞别语：再见；再会；祝您一路顺风；希望不久的将来还能在这里欢迎您。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3、求助于人语：请；请问；请帮忙；请帮助我一下；请多指教。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4、受人相助语：谢谢；麻烦你了；非常感谢！</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">5、得到感谢语：别客气；不用谢。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">6、打扰别人语：请原谅；对不起；给您添麻烦了；让您受累了。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">7、听到致歉语：不要紧；没关系；您不必介意。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">8、接待来客语：请进；请坐；请喝茶；再次见到您，真是十分高兴；欢迎光临。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">9、送别客人语：再见；慢走；欢迎再来。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">10、无力助人语：抱歉；实在对不起；请原谅。</span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">11</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、礼称别人语：老师；同志；先生；小姐；师傅；朋友。</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">12</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、提醒别人语：请您小心；请您注意；请您别急。</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">13</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、提醒行人语：请您注意安全；过路请走行人道。</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">14</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、慰问语：您辛苦了；让您受累了；给您添麻烦了。</span></span></p>\n<p -1.5=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">15</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、赞美语：您干得很好；太棒了；您真了不起；这太美了。</span></span></p>\n<p -2.0=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">16</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、征询语：我能为您做些什么吗？这样会不会打扰您？您还有别的事情吗？请借光；请您让一让好吗？</span></span></p>\n<p -2.0=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">17</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、道歉语：很抱歉！这件事实在没有办法做到；真不好意思&hellip;&hellip;；真对不起，让您久等了！对不起，打扰了！对不起，请稍候！</span></span></p>\n<p -2.0=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">18</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、应答语：行，请您稍候；好，马上就来；您不必客气，这是我应该做的；不用谢，照顾不周的地方请您多多包涵；请您吩咐。</span></span></p>\n<p -2.0=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">19</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、排队语：请大家自觉排队；请您排队好吗？</span></span></p>\n<p -2.0=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">20</span><span 10.5pt=\"\">、接打电话语：您好！我是&times;&times;&times;</span>，请讲话。谢谢，再见。</span></p>\n<p -2.0=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">公民基本道德规范</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">爱国守法 　明礼诚信　团结友善 　勤俭自强　敬业奉献</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">武汉市市民&ldquo;十不&rdquo;行为规范</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\">一、不随地吐痰；二、不乱倒乱扔废弃物；<br />\n	　　三、不乱贴乱画；四、不乱停放车辆；<br />\n	　　五、不乱穿马路；六、不乱搭乱盖；<br />\n	　　七、不损坏公共设施；八、不损害花草树木；<br />\n	　　九、不在公共场所吸烟十、不说脏话粗话</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1&#4;clip_image015.jpg\" /><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">&ldquo;三不&rdquo;与&ldquo;三管住&rdquo;</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">　　<span 10.5pt=\"\">一、不乱穿马路，管住自己的脚。<br />\n	　　二、不乱扔废弃物，管住自己的手。<br />\n	　　三、不说脏话粗话，管住自己的口。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">附：&ldquo;加强纪律教育，做文明一中人&rdquo;</span>督查工作安排</span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<table .5pt=\"\" 0cm=\"\" 5.4pt=\"\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" medium=\"\" solid=\"\" width=\"547\" windowtext=\"\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr exactly=\"\">\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">时</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">间</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">带队领导</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">参</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">加</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">人</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">员</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr exactly=\"\">\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">22</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">周</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">三</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">程盛怀</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">文</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">夏春花</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">郭大玉</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡跃进</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">方探锋</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr exactly=\"\">\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">23</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">周</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">四</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">沈新华</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">刘幼平</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">李红杰</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">郭大玉</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡跃进</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">方探锋</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr exactly=\"\">\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">24</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">周</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">五</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">张正喜</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">程</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">亮</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">李红杰</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">郭大玉</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡跃进</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">方探锋</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr exactly=\"\">\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">25</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">周</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">六</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">刘俊军</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">文</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">黄志奇</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">郭大玉</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡跃进</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">方探锋</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr exactly=\"\">\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">26</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">周</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">程盛怀</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">刘幼平</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">李红杰</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">郭大玉</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡跃进</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">方探锋</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr exactly=\"\">\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">27</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">周</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">一</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">刘双翼</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" 1.5=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">黄维舜</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">黄志奇</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">郭大玉</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡跃进</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">方探锋</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr exactly=\"\">\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">28</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">周</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">二</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">沈新华</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td 1pt=\"\" exactly=\"\" solid=\"\" windowtext=\"\">\n				<p 0cm=\"\" 2.0=\"\">\n					<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">刘幼平</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">郭大玉</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">胡跃进</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">方探锋</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">于志勇</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">说明：</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 2.0gd=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">．严禁学生在校园使用手机等移动通讯工具，禁止学生在教学区使用</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">MP3</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">MP4</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">等娱乐工具。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 2.0gd=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">．中午午休、下午放学、晚自习放学为带队集中巡查时间段（可在教导处集中），保卫巡逻人员近段时间全天候加强督查，特别是</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">5</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">00</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">?</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">：</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">30</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 2.0gd=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">3</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">．发现违纪情况，首先没收手机、</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">MP3</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">MP4</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">等物品，下发《违纪通知单》，然后通知班主任请家长来校带违纪学生回家教育三天，并全校通报批评，扣除该班</span><span 10.5pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">5</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">分。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1&#4;clip_image017.jpg\" /></span></p>\n','2','7','46',10,NULL,'2','1','2015-03-04 14:05:53','2015-03-04 14:05:53'),(132,'新洲一中择校生管理协议','','1','<p 0cm=\"\" align=\"center\" center=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">新洲一中择校生管理协议</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 7.8pt=\"\" none=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">择校生在新洲一中就读，享有同等的受教育权利，同时接受学校统一标准的考核和评价。学校尊重每个学生的成长机会，珍视每个学生的成才机遇。为了明确择校生的管理责任，特制订如下协议：</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">一、</span></strong><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">区外择校生家长须委托居住在邾城街道的亲友或我校教职工作为协助管理人，以帮助班主任和年级组对择校学生进行教育管理。协助管理人必须切实履行责任，负责做好学生、家长与班主任之间的联系沟通工作，关注学生的思想品行、生活及学习状况，发现不良倾向，应及时批评教育，不能借故推诿。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">二、</span></strong><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">择校学生必须严格遵守学校各项管理规定和纪律，注意培养良好的个人习惯，听从教育，热爱学习。择校学生入学第一学期为试读期，如不能适应本校学习、生活等方面管理，由班主任上报年级组审核，教导处审批做出解除附读关系的决定后，协助管理人须督促其家长将学生带离学校。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">三、</span></strong><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">借读学生须遵守本校各项规章制度，有下列情形之一者，班主任和协助管理人应通知其家长来校，共同教育学生认识问题，改正错误，并协商、研究整改措施，书面报年级组备案：</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、一月内迟到、早退累计达</span><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">10</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">次或旷课</span><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">天；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、一月内无故旷课达</span><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">6</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">课时或两月内无故旷课达</span><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">10</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">课时；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">3</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、一月内作业不能按时完成达</span><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">10</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">次或两月内达</span><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">16</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">次；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">4</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、发现有抽烟、喝酒等不良行为，经教育仍未改正；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">5</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、不能遵守课堂纪律或作息时间，经批评教育仍不能改正；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">6</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、打架、肇事但情节较轻微，尚未造成严重后果；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">7</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、在校使用手机等通讯工具；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">8</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、男女生交往过密，经教育仍不改正；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">9</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、进入营业性网吧，经教育仍不改正；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">10</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、仪表不合规范（异装、长发、染发、烫发、佩戴饰品等）；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">11</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、无故不参加学校、年级组织的各项活动，经教育不改；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">12</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、有其它违规行为，但情节轻微。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">四、</span></strong><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">有下列情形之一者，班主任和协助管理人须通知家长来校，解除附读关系，办理有关手续：</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">1</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、一学期内，有第三项所列两条以上（含两条）违纪行为；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">2</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、组织团伙打架肇事或打架肇事造成严重后果；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">3</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、采用恐吓、威胁手段强借强占他人财物；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">4</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、谈情说爱，造成不良影响，经教育仍不改正；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">5</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、经常进入营业性网吧，经教育仍不改正；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">6</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、未经批准在外租房住宿或夜不归宿；</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">7</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">、其它严重违纪违规行为。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong normal=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">五、</span></strong><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">择校生须一次交清规定费用，因故解除借读关系，除按学期（不满一学期按一学期计算）扣除有关费用外，余额按</span><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">80%</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">退还。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">此协议一式两份，双方各执一份，并共同遵守。</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" exactly=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">协议双方签名、盖章：</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 13.71gd=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">协助管理人：</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">教导处：</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 13.71gd=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 13.71gd=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">家</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">长：</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 13.71gd=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\" 13.71gd=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">200</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">年</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span><span 12pt=\"\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\">200</span></span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">年</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">月</span><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">日</span></span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=\"\" 0pt=\"\">\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p 0cm=